{"tid":2507557,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國新一階政府放寬禁令 中國留學生八月起可赴美","createTime":"2021-04-28T05:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T06:50:31.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa54207650ab4d7451d7a7ea74c8355bb6f07f80","tid":2507557,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:29:57.000Z","msg":"美國新一階政府放寬禁令 中國留學生八月起可赴美<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=432744&amp;fbclid=IwAR2KtGPh2GkiwLDVD9bOHr_M_VUJfooD7Jd--Bk4fAlNNQ06C5Ca5po-R4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432744%26fbclid%3DIwAR2KtGPh2GkiwLDVD9bOHr_M_VUJfooD7Jd--Bk4fAlNNQ06C5Ca5po-R4Y&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0qNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=8a8e5234\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432744%26fbclid%3DIwAR2KtGPh2GkiwLDVD9bOHr_M_VUJfooD7Jd--Bk4fAlNNQ06C5Ca5po-R4Y&h=d7950ed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=432744&amp;fbclid=IwAR2KtGPh2GkiwLDVD9bOHr_M_VUJfooD7Jd--Bk4fAlNNQ06C5Ca5po-R4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國最快八月讓中國留學生到當地上課。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發布通知，指由八月開始，持有有效F-1或M-1簽證的人員，可以乘坐直航航班入境美國，而毋須事先聯繫使館申請「國家利益豁免條件」。<br />\n<br />\n因應新冠疫情，美國目前禁止兩星期內到過中國、巴西、南非、伊朗及部分歐洲國家的大部分非美國公民入境，上月率才放寬對歐洲學生的相關限制，如今進一步為上述包括中國等地的學生放行，他們可以在今年秋季學期開始前30天內到美國。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國現行規定，所有入境者必須持最近72小時新冠病毒陰性檢測證明。"},{"pid":"57df524a6aa06c4a46627db3e45df4d667ec03a1","tid":2507557,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T05:30:58.000Z","msg":"點睇Joe 上台後，中共企業赴美國IPO速度創出紀錄？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2504417/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2504417/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bc628301ffa8dd824b0b8132844c89f1fba08281","tid":2507557,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T06:45:01.000Z","msg":"外匯流出 人才流走<br />\n支持多啲中國學生去